---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Claim Guardians LLC | Maximizes Your Property Insurance Settlement in Florida" 
  description="Insurance companies underpay property damage claims. Claim Guardians forces your insurer to pay your maximum legal entitlement. You pay zero upfront fees."
>
  <!-- 2. Hero Section -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-8 leading-tight">
        Claim Guardians Maximizes Your Property Insurance Settlement in Florida.
      </h1>
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-700 font-medium mb-12 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        Insurance companies underpay property damage claims. Claim Guardians forces your insurer to pay your maximum legal entitlement. You pay zero upfront fees. We collect our fee only after you receive your check.
      </h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 mb-12">
        <a href="/free-claim-review" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white bg-blue-600 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/20 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-100">
          Get a Free Claim Review
        </a>
        <a href="tel:5551234567" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 rounded-xl hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
          Emergency? Call Us Now
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Trust Indicators -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
          Florida Licensed Adjusters (FAPIA)
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 15h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v6z"/></svg>
          BBB A+ Rating
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-yellow-500">
          ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ <span class="text-slate-600 ml-1">5-Star Reviews</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. Quick Solution Grid -->
  <section class="bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-200 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          Claim Guardians Resolves Every Type of Property Damage.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
          Property owners face complex insurance policies. Our licensed public adjusters simplify the claims process. Select your damage type below.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <a href="/services/water-damage" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">💧</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Water & Leak Damage</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Claim Guardians uncovers hidden moisture and burst pipe damage.</p>
        </a>
        
        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <a href="/services/hurricane-damage" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌪️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Hurricane & Storm Damage</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Our experts evaluate wind, hail, and severe weather impacts.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <a href="/services/roof-damage" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🏠</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Roof Leak & Damage</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">We prove structural roof failures to stubborn insurers.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Card 4 -->
        <a href="/services/fire-damage" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🔥</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Fire & Smoke Damage</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Our team assesses structural loss and toxic smoke damage.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Card 5 -->
        <a href="/services/mold-claims" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🦠</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Mold Damage</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Claim Guardians documents toxic mold growth after water exposure.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Card 6 -->
        <a href="/services/denied-claims" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">❌</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Denied & Underpaid Claims</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">We appeal unfair insurance decisions and demand full payment.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. Social Proof -->
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-16 text-center">
        Claim Guardians Delivers Real Financial Results.
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm font-bold rounded-full mb-4">
              Water Damage in Miami, FL
            </span>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-lg">
                <span class="text-slate-500 font-medium">Insurance Initial Offer:</span>
                <span class="text-red-500/70 line-through font-bold">~$14,500</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xl">
                <span class="text-slate-900 font-bold">Claim Guardians Settlement:</span>
                <span class="text-green-600 font-extrabold bg-green-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg">$82,300</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="text-slate-700 italic border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
            "The insurance company offered pennies for my flooded kitchen. Claim Guardians handled all the stressful calls and secured enough money to fix everything properly."
            <footer class="mt-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">– Maria S.</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm font-bold rounded-full mb-4">
              Roof Damage in Fort Myers, FL
            </span>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-lg">
                <span class="text-slate-500 font-medium">Insurance Initial Offer:</span>
                <span class="text-red-500/70 font-bold">Claim Denied</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xl">
                <span class="text-slate-900 font-bold">Claim Guardians Settlement:</span>
                <span class="text-green-600 font-extrabold bg-green-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg">$65,000</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="text-slate-700 italic border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
            "My insurer denied my storm damage claim completely. Claim Guardians found the hidden proof and forced the company to pay for a full roof replacement."
            <footer class="mt-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">– David L.</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 5. How We Work -->
  <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-16 text-center">
        Claim Guardians Manages Your Entire Claim Process.
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 relative">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="relative z-10 bg-blue-800/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-blue-700">
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-blue-500 mb-6 opacity-50">01</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Free Property Inspection.</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">
            Claim Guardians inspects your property for free. Our state-licensed adjusters document all hidden damages.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="relative z-10 bg-blue-800/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-blue-700">
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-blue-500 mb-6 opacity-50">02</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">We Handle the Insurance.</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">
            Our team files your claim paperwork. We negotiate the maximum payout directly with your insurance company.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="relative z-10 bg-blue-800/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-blue-700">
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-blue-500 mb-6 opacity-50">03</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">You Get Paid.</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">
            You receive your settlement check. Claim Guardians collects a fee only after you get paid.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 6. Objection Handling -->
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-16 text-center">
        Claim Guardians Protects You, Not the Insurance Company.
      </h2>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden border border-slate-200">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
          <!-- Column 1: The Insurer -->
          <div class="p-10 bg-red-50/50 md:border-r border-slate-200 relative">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-900 mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600">✗</span>
              The Insurance Company's Adjuster
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-6">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">⚠️</span>
                <span class="text-slate-700 text-lg font-medium">The insurance corporation pays them.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">⚠️</span>
                <span class="text-slate-700 text-lg font-medium">They protect the insurer's corporate budget.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">⚠️</span>
                <span class="text-slate-700 text-lg font-medium">They use legal jargon to limit your payout.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Column 2: Us -->
          <div class="p-10 bg-blue-600 text-white relative">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-blue-600">✓</span>
              Claim Guardians (Your Public Adjuster)
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-6">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-blue-200 mt-1">✨</span>
                <span class="text-lg font-medium">You hire Claim Guardians.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-blue-200 mt-1">🛡️</span>
                <span class="text-lg font-medium">We protect your family and your property.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-blue-200 mt-1">💰</span>
                <span class="text-lg font-medium">We maximize your financial settlement.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 7. Frequently Asked Questions -->
  <section class="bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-12 text-center">
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <!-- FAQ 1 -->
        <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-xl text-slate-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">
            <span>How much does a public adjuster cost in Florida?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed border-t border-transparent group-open:border-slate-100 group-open:pt-4">
            Claim Guardians charges $0 in upfront fees. Clients pay a contingency fee only after they receive their settlement. Florida state law caps public adjuster fees at 20% for standard claims.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 2 -->
        <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-xl text-slate-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">
            <span>When should I hire a public adjuster?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed border-t border-transparent group-open:border-slate-100 group-open:pt-4">
            Property owners should hire a public adjuster immediately after discovering property damage. However, you can hire Claim Guardians even if the insurance company already denied your claim.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 3 -->
        <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-xl text-slate-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">
            <span>What is the difference between an independent adjuster and a public adjuster?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed border-t border-transparent group-open:border-slate-100 group-open:pt-4">
            The insurance company hires an independent adjuster to protect their corporate budget. You hire a public adjuster to maximize your financial payout. Claim Guardians represents the policyholder exclusively.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
